citations:
    citation-adwd-daenerys-ii:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "Daenerys II"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Daenerys Targaryen. Daenerys continues ruling Meereen. She holds court and hears more petitioners. The Sons of the Harpy (insurgent slavers) have been murdering freedmen and Unsullied in the streets. Hizdahr zo Loraq again presses her to reopen the fighting pits, arguing it will buy peace with the old slaver families. Daenerys is attracted to Daario Naharis. She refuses to marry Hizdahr at this point. The tension between keeping Meereen and sailing for Westeros is a central conflict."
